name: Paper Fly
description:
"Keep the paper plane undercontrol don't let it crash!"

A paper airplane flying freely in the air. Control the plane to fly and avoid various obstacles!. A game where players must control a plane to avoid various obstacles and score as many points as possible.  

Please fill this feedback form after playing our game. We would really appreciate it! Anyways, thank you for playing our game ❤️

"Buat pesawat kertas jangan tetap dibawah kendali, jangan biarkan hancur!"

Sebuah pesawat kertas terbang dengan bebas di udara. Bantu kendalikan pesawat untuk terbang dan menghindari berbagai rintangan!. Sebuah game dimana pemain harus mengendalikan pesawat untuk menghindari berbagai rintangan dan mencetak score sebanyak banyaknya.

Isi Form Feedback setelah bermain game kami!, terimakasih banyak👀
